snippet.title: Outnumbered
snippet.description:
Outnumbered is a competitive target shooting video game specifically engineered to drive traffic to your venue by rewarding people every time they play.  

Players unlock in-game content after each stage, which they can use to create and upgrade custom weapons in the game’s free companion app. 
Pop culture themes, live leaderboards and an endless combination of weapons provides broad appeal to both casual and hardcore gamers. 

Outnumbered will keep players coming back to your venue time and time again.
